@story
Feature: Create Story

  Background: set connection to pivotal tracker API REST
    Given I have set a connection to pivotal tracker API service
    And I have the next parameters to create a project:

      | name   | project to create stories |
      | public | true                      |

    And I send a POST request to /projects endpoint

  Scenario: Create a story
    Given I have a project created
    And I have the story endpoint
    And I have the next parameters to create a story:

      | name        | story example          |
      | description | example of description |

    When I send a story POST request to /stories endpoint
    Then I expect the status code 200
